column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,s.instrument,g.EW_OIII_# FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN emissionLinesPort g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE  cModelMag_g># and cModelMag_g<# and  psfMag_g<# and cModelMagErr_g<# and  cModelMagErr_r<# and cModelMag_g - cModelMag_r > # and psfMag_g -psfMag_r > # and  cModelMag_r - cModelMag_i > # and psfMag_r -psfMag_i > # and petroR9#_r<# and petroR9#_r ># and petrorad_g< # and EW_OIII_# > #
